the bait ( french : l'appât ) , also known as fresh bait , is a 1995 french film directed by bertrand tavernier about two boys and a girl who commit a murder , with the girl acting as a ' bait ' . the film is based on the 1990 book of the same name by morgan sportès , which is in turn based on the " valérie subra affair " , a true event that happened in 1984 .